snippet.title: Gas Station Simulator - Can Touch This DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
The first DLC for Gas Station Simulator "Can Touch This" will be available on May 18!

You can take interior and exterior customization to an entirely new level in the DLC! 

Take matters into your hand. Almost literally. 
With the help of your new, trusty hammer, it's time to redecorate as you've never done before. 

Refurbish walls to your heart's content, changing their features and decor as you see fit.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1940030/Gas_Station_Simulator__Can_Touch_This_DLC/

Make sure to add the game to your wishlist!

Follow our development progress on our social media 👇 

Discord: https://discord.gg/mcXjfHrtgT
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GasStationSim
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/gasstationsimulator

Have fun, and let us know what you think!!!
